$ R function arguments: ellipsis

{ Accessing values

  The values that were passed to a → development/languages/R/function[function] via the ellipsis construct can be access with `list(...)` within the function body.

  gh|about-r|/function/arguments/ellipsis/access-values.R||

}
{ Determining the names of the arguments

  The names of the arguments that were passed can be determined with the → development/languages/R/functions/names[`names(…)`] function:

  gh|about-r|/function/arguments/ellipsis/argument-names.R||

}
sa:
  → development/languages/R/function/arguments[Function arguments]
